                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="walk-thru-step">
            <div class="diagnostic-content-wrapper">
                <img id='shrink-me' src="/images/tools/diagnostic/diagnostic_intro_slide_2.svg" alt="diagnostic image">
                <div class="diagnostic-blurb">
                    <h2>Student Responses Analyzed</h2>
                    <p>
                        Quill automatically analyzes and grades open-ended responses. It identifies the writing skills students know and the skills they need to practice.
                    </p>
