                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="tool-carousel">
        <div id="diagnosticCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">

            <a class="left carousel-control" href="#diagnosticCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>

            <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
            <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
                <div class="item active">
                  <div class="wrapper">
                    <img src="/images/tools/Diagnostic1.png" alt="Chania">
                  </div>
                  <p>The diagnostic assesses students and then automatically builds a personalized learning plan for each student.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                  <div class="wrapper">
                    <img src="/images/tools/Diagnostic2.png" alt="Chania">
                  </div>
                  <p>The diagnostic covers a number of critical sentence structure skills, such as fragments and run-on sentences. In this exercise, students use the dependent clause to write a complete sentence.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                  <div class="wrapper">
                    <img src="/images/tools/Diagnostic3.png" alt="Chania">
                  </div>
                  <p>In this exercise, students transform a run-on sentence into a complete sentence.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                  <div class="wrapper">
                    <img src="/images/tools/Diagnostic4.png" alt="Chania">
                  </div>
                  <p>Teachers see reports that state exactly which errors the students made.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Left and right controls -->

            <a class="right carousel-control" href="#diagnosticCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>

            <!-- Indicators -->
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <li data-target="#diagnosticCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                <li data-target="#diagnosticCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                <li data-target="#diagnosticCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                <li data-target="#diagnosticCarousel" data-slide-to="3"></li>
            </ol>

        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="tool-try-it bg-darkred bg-image-diagnostic-pattern">
        <h2 class='q-h1'>Try It Yourself!</h2>
        <a href='https://quillconnect.firebaseapp.com/#/play/diagnostic/fNAwNLJDkc2T8O5lBeJQwg' class="q-button cta-button bg-white text-darkred">Preview the Diagnostic</a>
    </section>

    <section class="tool-testimonial">
        <!-- <img class='q-headshot' src="/images/daniel_scibienski_90.png" alt="Daniel Scibienski"> -->
        <p class='quote'>
            "It was very useful to see which concepts students needed more help with. It is extremely beneficial if I want to work on grouping students based on skill."
        </p>
        <h4 class="q-h4 author">
